{"tid":762705,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好消息！港澳通行證「L 簽」可以自由行出境啦！","createTime":"2018-07-31T13:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T10:34:35.000Z","uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bf20bd53c5b40021d7c5d35296937f3900aef35d","tid":762705,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:37:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/kknews.cc/zh-hk/travel/bqnqlao.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Ftravel%2Fbqnqlao.amp&d=rbotY4UwvtV8%2BbxlHH5kJ8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=00d12885\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/kknews.cc/zh-hk/travel/bqnqlao.amp</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2017年8月5日起，經所有口岸去香港的「L」簽注的團隊旅客，已經不再經旅行社團簽過關，持卡者可選擇自助過關，持舊本子需要在人工通道過關，L 簽證件不再經旅行收費簽證過關!什麼是 G 簽和 L 簽？<br />\n內地居民前往香港遊玩，需要辦理「一證一簽」，即《往來港澳通行證》和旅行簽注。簽注分為 G 簽和 L 簽，G 簽代表自由行簽，L 簽代表團簽。<br />\n<br />\n開通港澳自由行城市的居民，辦理 G 簽即可前往香港。<br />\n如果不是自由行城市的居民或者不符合自由行條件的居民，那就得選擇辦理 L 簽，也就是要跟團出入境，而且這種類型是不能內地直接飛到香港的。<br />\n<br />\n實際上，「跟團出入境」並不是必須跟團游，找旅行社幫忙，做一份去港澳團隊旅遊的名單，持有該名單，就可以過關了。<br />\n所以很多人在淘寶上買好跟團出入境（也就是大家說的買送關，或叫做名單），或者去到口岸送關，但價格比網上貴很多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以後持 L 簽的內地居民，以後去香港可以省下一筆買團簽的費用了，但只有新版卡式通行證可以自助通關，舊版本式的還是要走人工通道過關。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"1566fe0fbf1a0244c14526ba6f31f6a9ebb0eff6","tid":762705,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:38:04.000Z","msg":"屌支那人老母！"},{"pid":"5f38f0e80a44cc4cfad6cbd4cc64fbfb6fb49e11","tid":762705,"uid":84751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:27:17.000Z","msg":"唔怪得之咁撚多支那襲港"},{"pid":"f5a990f356aff108bc8cda752c8511b81f1cd543","tid":762705,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T10:34:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}